{"tid":2249324,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今年grad但仲係唔知自己做緊啲乜","createTime":"2020-10-19T09:19:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-14T08:47:37.000Z","uid":153877,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d53c87ae82c17a381cf0810db8f60c6ca9a70c15","tid":2249324,"uid":153877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T09:19:47.000Z","msg":"頭先見住男朋友上網填form搵intern，就覺得自己好撚垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我同男朋友都係英國讀書<br />\n但我大學讀個科又唔專，乜柒都有讀啲咁<br />\nintern又無返過 淨係返過下珍珠奶茶鋪、sales 咁<br />\n暑假又淨係係到hea同讀online course <br />\n<br />\n話為興趣，做緊同自學緊好多design嘅嘢。但其實自己都仲係好撚廢，今年先真正學<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />遲啲如果拎嚟接freelance 都唔知有無人會用我，仲學緊入門嘢，淨係得個心好想做。<br />\n<br />\n屋企人叫我讀taught master 但design好似無master讀，而我本身個科如果讀master又係囇尻氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n男朋友好叻，英文講得好好，又有經驗。佢仲有3年讀，要留係英國發展絕對無問題（加上佢自己都想）。但對比起我今年grad，英文垃圾又無工作經驗，唔夠膽走出自己嘅comfort zone。香港變成咁都仲想返香港做嘢。<br />\n<br />\n望住男朋友就覺得自己真係好撚垃圾好想喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我完全唔知點算好，返香港做嘢但又無返過intern。留係英國又會好驚。 <br />\n我好想可以同男朋友一齊行落去，但佢想留英國我想返香港係未一定分手收場<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我係未應該放生男朋友等佢搵個配得上佢嘅女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌 好多嘢煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e5cda153cfd8fa3725375ce872d0f79dcef8d8a","tid":2249324,"uid":136049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T13:45:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67c54e82266cc47a6c589fe8e08b0032fce11834","tid":2249324,"uid":153877,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9e5cda153cfd8fa3725375ce872d0f79dcef8d8a","tid":2249324,"uid":136049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T13:45:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T14:14:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f279f5cf24e01843f0c00108e61ddd8b888798b7","tid":2249324,"uid":258921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T14:30:46.000Z","msg":"樓主咁驚當初點interview part-time"},{"pid":"153ba213e023c83f61fa8e8df7c3642bc6b534b7","tid":2249324,"uid":85774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T14:34:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"939f3fa95c19ff924b76e55671828e886fd23ace","tid":2249324,"uid":153877,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f279f5cf24e01843f0c00108e61ddd8b888798b7","tid":2249324,"uid":258921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T14:30:46.000Z","msg":"樓主咁驚當初點interview part-time"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T15:19:26.000Z","msg":"間part-time 香港人開<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06d63cd648ffc53438220a64fb799747d68c229e","tid":2249324,"uid":153877,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"153ba213e023c83f61fa8e8df7c3642bc6b534b7","tid":2249324,"uid":85774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T14:34:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T15:20:59.000Z","msg":"可摸耳問吓 你最後留咗係美國發展定返嚟香港呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86fe09a25e90027befeb67851fbfd548e4b81301","tid":2249324,"uid":85774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06d63cd648ffc53438220a64fb799747d68c229e","tid":2249324,"uid":153877,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"153ba213e023c83f61fa8e8df7c3642bc6b534b7","tid":2249324,"uid":85774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T14:34:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T15:20:59.000Z","msg":"可摸耳問吓 你最後留咗係美國發展定返嚟香港呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T07:45:17.000Z","msg":"美國做咗一年 返咗嚟"},{"pid":"20e5e004adf7a1c9fe1addca76457ffed23fb196","tid":2249324,"uid":105833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T08:47:37.000Z","msg":"加油呀<br />\n唔好太自卑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你男朋友之所以仲留喺你身邊<br />\n證明你一定有啲佢欣賞嘅地方<br />\n既然你已經知道自己嘅不足就努力改善下啦"}]}